articles.title: Historical accomplishment: Modi hails Indian women's badminton team - Rediff.com
articles.description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi hailed as 'historical accomplishment' Indian women shuttlers winning the Badminton Asia Team Championships, and said the way our 'nari shakti' (women power) has been excelling in various sports is phenomenal.
